name: Marquette University
WICU: 958th  thumb The university includes 11 schools and colleges: Helen Way Klingler College of Arts and Sciences, College of Business Administration, J. William and Mary Diederich College of Communication, College of Education, College of Engineering, College of Health Sciences, College of Nursing, College of Professional Studies, Graduate School, Marquette University School of Dentistry, and Marquette University Law School.  Marquette's largest college is the Helen Way Klingler College of Arts and Sciences. |
